<% layout("/layouts/privacyBoilerplate.ejs") %>


  <div class="bg-dark text-white text-center p-5">
    <h1 class="fw-bold">aircover</h1>
  </div>


  <div class="container my-5">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-8">
        <h2>AirCover for guests</h2>
        <p>Every home booking comes with AirCover for guests. If there’s a serious issue with your Airbnb home that your host can’t resolve, we’re here to help.</p>

        <h5 class="text-danger">We’ll help you get rebooked or give you a full or partial refund</h5>
        <p>Here’s where we can help:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>If your home host cancels before check-in</li>
          <li>If there’s a problem and you can’t get in touch with your host</li>
          <li>If the listing is significantly different than advertised, and your host can’t resolve the issue</li>
        </ul>

        <p>Our team can help you find a similar place, considering location and amenities, based on availability at comparable pricing. If a similar place isn’t available or you’d prefer not to rebook, we’ll give you a full or partial refund, including service fees.</p>

        <h4 class="mt-4">How AirCover for guests works</h4>
        <ul class="list-group">
          <li class="list-group-item">Host cancels your reservation prior to check-in</li>
          <li class="list-group-item">The heating is not working in winter</li>
          <li class="list-group-item">The listing has fewer bedrooms than listed</li>
          <li class="list-group-item">A different type of home—a private room instead of an entire home</li>
          <li class="list-group-item">A major advertised amenity, such as a pool or kitchen, is missing</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3 text-muted">AirCover for guests doesn’t include more minor inconveniences, like a broken toaster.</p>
      </div>
>
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="card shadow-sm">
          <div class="card-body text-center">
            <h5>Need help with a reservation?</h5>
            <button class="btn btn-danger mt-3">Log in or sign up</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

